sql_json.natural_language: Find the last time adrian@rancilio.co.za emailed julie@lineagecoffee.com.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE fromEmail = 'adrian@rancilio.co.za' AND 'julie@lineagecoffee.com' IN UNNEST(toEmails) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
